00:06:59.992 --> 00:07:02.992
more in charge than you as he uses

00:07:03.033 --> 00:07:05.994
vivid examples and pithy quotes to rule

00:07:06.014 --> 00:07:08.454
with you.

00:07:08.994 --> 00:07:10.894
Genesis, the first book of the Torah.

00:07:10.915 --> 00:07:13.096
Now we're in the third chapter, three,

00:07:13.175 --> 00:07:13.675
sixteen.

00:07:15.406 --> 00:07:17.288
So when we consider God's pronouncement

