00:10:08.581 --> 00:10:11.922
Chawa would be driven by shashuka,

00:10:12.442 --> 00:10:14.841
emotional feelings and strong desires.

00:10:15.802 --> 00:10:18.163
This would then require man to do a

00:10:18.202 --> 00:10:20.663
