00:10:26.625 --> 00:10:29.505
man would have to lead and he would

00:10:29.546 --> 00:10:30.426
have to educate.

00:10:32.126 --> 00:10:33.647
Therefore, through this narrative,

00:10:33.706 --> 00:10:36.567
Yawa was telling us what went wrong in

00:10:36.587 --> 00:10:37.607
