00:13:13.595 --> 00:13:15.677
Lesson six, engage.

00:13:16.535 --> 00:13:19.517
Make a contribution if you want to impress

00:13:19.557 --> 00:13:22.077
God, if you want to earn his trust.

00:13:23.359 --> 00:13:24.379
Lesson seven,

00:13:24.999 --> 00:13:26.480
if you want to understand Yahweh,

00:13:27.179 --> 00:13:31.701
be especially observant and contemplative.

00:13:31.761 --> 00:13:32.602
So in this case,

00:13:33.123 --> 00:13:36.083
the fall of man became inevitable because

00:13:36.244 --> 00:13:38.345
Adam did not listen and he showed no

00:13:38.404 --> 00:13:38.945
initiative.

00:13:40.285 --> 00:13:42.407
The man paid no attention to anything God

00:13:42.447 --> 00:13:45.488
said and he contributed nothing.

00:13:46.677 --> 00:13:49.958
essentially destroying the relationship

00:13:51.259 --> 00:13:54.279
humankind has consistently valued its own

00:13:54.340 --> 00:13:57.379
rhetoric over yahweh's instructions

00:13:58.059 --> 00:14:01.100
religion is the consequence moreover

00:14:01.721 --> 00:14:04.221
religion has backfired on women in

00:14:04.261 --> 00:14:06.682
particular because it is used by men to

00:14:06.822 --> 00:14:09.383
control them the difference between

00:14:09.543 --> 00:14:12.942
teaching and tyranny is not only enormous

00:14:13.602 --> 00:14:15.504
the value of one and the cost of

00:14:15.524 --> 00:14:15.923
the other

00:14:16.889 --> 00:14:19.750
is the lesson that humanity has long

00:14:19.830 --> 00:14:24.991
failed to grasp.

00:14:25.011 --> 00:14:27.751
Yahweh's issue with mankind is habitual

00:14:27.792 --> 00:14:29.952
behavior rather than a chance mistake,

00:14:29.993 --> 00:14:31.553
and that has become evident throughout

00:14:31.594 --> 00:14:32.394
this instruction.

00:14:33.734 --> 00:14:36.934
The teaching regarding the tree was

00:14:38.056 --> 00:14:40.515
consistently conveyed in the imperfect

00:14:40.556 --> 00:14:42.716
conjugation, which is to say,

00:14:42.736 --> 00:14:45.278
don't continually devour it.

00:14:46.447 --> 00:14:48.469
But both Chawa and Adam admitted that

00:14:49.448 --> 00:14:51.190
their consumption was ongoing.

00:14:51.210 --> 00:14:51.629
In fact,

00:14:51.669 --> 00:14:54.051
we found Adam hanging out in the tree

00:14:54.091 --> 00:14:56.251
when Yahweh questioned him.

00:14:57.251 --> 00:14:59.653
The reason that this is important is that

00:14:59.692 --> 00:15:03.514
we are no longer guilty of poor judgment

00:15:04.153 --> 00:15:06.154
once we learn from our mistakes and choose

00:15:06.195 --> 00:15:08.676
a better course of action.

00:15:09.115 --> 00:15:10.157
I was once religious.

00:15:10.236 --> 00:15:11.277
I was once political.

00:15:11.397 --> 00:15:11.976
I am neither.

00:15:12.496 --> 00:15:14.077
I'm not guilty of either anymore.

00:15:15.421 --> 00:15:17.201
Now this is why Yahweh asks us to

00:15:17.261 --> 00:15:19.581
walk away from the confounding nature of

00:15:19.642 --> 00:15:22.283
Babel, country and religion,

00:15:22.342 --> 00:15:24.724
the intermixing of politics and religion,

00:15:25.364 --> 00:15:27.443
rather than insist that we never venture

00:15:27.484 --> 00:15:30.345
in that direction in the first place.

00:15:30.945 --> 00:15:32.865
It's so much better when God just says,

00:15:33.166 --> 00:15:34.446
stop doing that thing.

00:15:36.866 --> 00:15:37.626
Now this note,

00:15:38.787 --> 00:15:41.128
it is one thing to have been misled

00:15:41.248 --> 00:15:43.729
and then to have come upon the truth.

00:15:44.658 --> 00:15:48.020
giving up the religious lie for the joys

00:15:48.061 --> 00:15:49.001
of a relationship.

00:15:50.022 --> 00:15:52.043
And that's important.

00:15:52.624 --> 00:15:56.605
We are being encouraged to forego having

00:15:56.645 --> 00:15:57.386
been misled,

00:15:57.706 --> 00:16:00.187
to cling to the truth once we know

00:16:00.227 --> 00:16:03.429
it and to give up the deceptions that

00:16:03.450 --> 00:16:04.410
have led us astray.

00:16:05.150 --> 00:16:05.571
But of course,

00:16:05.610 --> 00:16:08.352
it's another to have been shown what

00:16:08.393 --> 00:16:09.553
Yahweh expects of us,

00:16:10.394 --> 00:16:12.796
to have embraced it and then to turn

00:16:12.875 --> 00:16:13.336
against it.

00:16:14.376 --> 00:16:18.177
which you had learned to somehow satiate a

00:16:18.258 --> 00:16:19.278
personal desire.

00:16:21.619 --> 00:16:23.139
And that's what happened in the garden.

00:16:25.100 --> 00:16:30.061
There is no revolving door to God's home.

00:16:31.861 --> 00:16:33.721
You can enter the covenant on Yahweh's

00:16:33.761 --> 00:16:36.602
terms and you can leave it on yours.

00:16:38.484 --> 00:16:39.303
But if you do,

00:16:39.384 --> 00:16:40.604
there is no coming back.

00:16:42.205 --> 00:16:43.085
You will have proven

00:16:44.926 --> 00:16:49.268
that you cannot be trusted.

00:16:49.288 --> 00:16:51.447
We're reminded that this whole story

00:16:51.488 --> 00:16:53.469
played out around the Tree of Knowledge.

00:16:53.649 --> 00:16:57.429
Its fruit was for another time and for

00:16:57.549 --> 00:16:58.571
other individuals.

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:00.510
But even then,

00:17:01.131 --> 00:17:05.692
to covet it and then reject it is

00:17:05.712 --> 00:17:08.074
a crime with a serious consequence and

00:17:08.114 --> 00:17:11.815
cost.

00:17:11.835 --> 00:17:12.935
By prematurely

00:17:14.747 --> 00:17:18.490
releasing evil on a world equipped to,

00:17:19.111 --> 00:17:20.632
or ill-equipped, I should say,

00:17:20.731 --> 00:17:23.614
to suppress it with sound instruction.

00:17:24.694 --> 00:17:25.415
Ha-adamah,

00:17:25.455 --> 00:17:27.757
the earth was cursed for a long time

00:17:28.758 --> 00:17:31.339
as the growth of man was stymied.

00:17:32.861 --> 00:17:35.022
We became particularly annoying to God.

00:17:35.083 --> 00:17:37.945
He was frustrated that he had even

00:17:38.006 --> 00:17:39.586
conceived us, regretting it.

00:17:40.759 --> 00:17:42.800
The most debilitating of the plagues would

00:17:43.361 --> 00:17:46.563
be man's propensity to conceive gods in

00:17:46.623 --> 00:17:47.304
man's image.

00:17:48.224 --> 00:17:48.884
And of course,

00:17:49.325 --> 00:17:50.506
through no fault of his own,

00:17:50.546 --> 00:17:53.489
it would make the job of the Atama,

00:17:53.548 --> 00:17:55.349
this bloody red man of the earth,

00:17:56.371 --> 00:17:57.612
all the more difficult,

00:17:57.991 --> 00:18:00.114
even at times exasperating and

00:18:00.334 --> 00:18:01.394
infuriating.

00:18:02.194 --> 00:18:04.416
So many lies to impugn.

00:18:06.394 --> 00:18:08.214
The surest way to prove one's worth with

00:18:08.275 --> 00:18:09.815
God is to engage,

00:18:10.474 --> 00:18:11.635
offering something of value.

00:18:12.736 --> 00:18:14.436
As was the case with the ark,

00:18:15.237 --> 00:18:17.518
Yahweh has provided a full set of

00:18:17.557 --> 00:18:18.218
instructions.

00:18:19.538 --> 00:18:21.199
So now the burden really is on us.

00:18:21.798 --> 00:18:24.319
We can either act or God will pass

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:27.020
us by and he will find someone who

00:18:27.060 --> 00:18:28.280
will listen and engage.

00:18:29.441 --> 00:18:33.442
Lazy and listless dependents are just

00:18:33.702 --> 00:18:34.603
lousy partners.

00:18:35.830 --> 00:18:36.330
Therefore,

00:18:36.872 --> 00:18:39.874
for one's life to become two lives,

00:18:40.934 --> 00:18:43.116
we must contribute during the first of

00:18:43.136 --> 00:18:43.336
them.

00:18:46.419 --> 00:18:47.901
Such are the lessons of the garden.

00:18:48.941 --> 00:18:52.084
Such has been the case with the

00:18:52.324 --> 00:18:54.865
reestablishment and growth of the tree of

00:18:54.905 --> 00:18:55.346
knowledge.

00:18:56.788 --> 00:18:58.868
It is why the story has been told

00:18:58.949 --> 00:18:59.549
this way.

00:19:01.010 --> 00:19:02.372
And I hope you're wiser for it.

00:19:04.471 --> 00:19:05.711
It is seldom discussed,

00:19:06.452 --> 00:19:08.374
mostly as a result of misleading

00:19:08.413 --> 00:19:09.255
translations,

00:19:10.414 --> 00:19:14.258
but Adam and Chawa were assessed and

00:19:14.298 --> 00:19:16.039
treated quite similarly.

00:19:17.641 --> 00:19:20.303
Ishibon was applied to both.

00:19:21.683 --> 00:19:24.465
Life would be challenging by design and

00:19:24.526 --> 00:19:26.426
necessity for man and woman.

00:19:28.288 --> 00:19:29.829
This is God's intent.

00:19:30.676 --> 00:19:32.557
since we were told at the outset that

00:19:32.719 --> 00:19:35.201
Adam was placed in the garden to pay

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:38.502
attention to it and to work in it.

00:19:39.364 --> 00:19:42.987
Contributory labor and productive industry

00:19:43.886 --> 00:19:47.569
is not a punishment because work has its

00:19:47.630 --> 00:19:48.310
rewards.

00:19:48.911 --> 00:19:50.732
It's highly valued by God.

00:19:51.613 --> 00:19:54.335
Life's greatest achievements are produced

00:19:54.414 --> 00:19:56.156
when we collaborate with Yahweh.

00:19:57.267 --> 00:19:57.987
Doe David,

00:19:58.027 --> 00:20:00.048
who is the exemplar for us all,

00:20:00.448 --> 00:20:02.907
was often called Yahweh's Ebed,

00:20:03.848 --> 00:20:04.669
his coworker.

00:20:08.430 --> 00:20:09.130
Well, in the garden,

00:20:09.789 --> 00:20:12.750
Adam was clearly coddled.

00:20:12.770 --> 00:20:16.071
That would not be the case once dismissed

00:20:16.112 --> 00:20:16.412
from it.

00:20:17.551 --> 00:20:18.912
And yet amidst the briars,

00:20:19.032 --> 00:20:20.373
a choder would emerge.

00:20:21.220 --> 00:20:22.201
from ha-adamah,

00:20:22.980 --> 00:20:24.803
and eventually restore the relationship.

00:20:25.403 --> 00:20:26.584
Well, at least for some.

00:20:27.765 --> 00:20:30.185
This, like so much of the Torah,

00:20:30.967 --> 00:20:33.949
is written such that what begins harshly

00:20:35.069 --> 00:20:38.751
can lead in one or two directions to

00:20:39.712 --> 00:20:43.536
degeneration and death or restoration in

00:20:43.596 --> 00:20:43.895
life.

00:20:45.797 --> 00:20:46.577
The choice is yours.

00:20:49.813 --> 00:20:51.814
The text of Bar Reshith,

00:20:51.953 --> 00:20:53.895
Genesis three reads,

00:20:55.557 --> 00:20:59.019
Disgusting thorn bushes that do not bear

00:20:59.058 --> 00:21:02.740
fruit, detestable and loathsome,

00:21:02.882 --> 00:21:03.761
unpredictable,

00:21:04.261 --> 00:21:06.564
unproductive vegetation and abhorrent,

00:21:07.263 --> 00:21:08.384
irritating plants,

00:21:08.484 --> 00:21:12.968
twisted and splinter like as an awakening

00:21:13.008 --> 00:21:13.689
during the summer.

00:21:14.545 --> 00:21:17.726
and thistles used to goad and control

00:21:17.826 --> 00:21:18.846
prickly plants,

00:21:19.227 --> 00:21:21.468
which are of no value and are used

00:21:21.508 --> 00:21:22.568
to restrict access,

00:21:22.608 --> 00:21:25.890
which choke out the productive plants,

00:21:25.910 --> 00:21:26.890
it will produce for you.

00:21:28.871 --> 00:21:31.972
So you will consume these plants of the

00:21:32.073 --> 00:21:33.053
open environs.

00:21:34.354 --> 00:21:35.794
By the sweat of your brow,

00:21:35.834 --> 00:21:40.076
you will eat bread and you will devour

00:21:40.115 --> 00:21:41.757
war, a call like him.

00:21:43.916 --> 00:21:47.480
until the restoring witness returns to

00:21:47.519 --> 00:21:48.221
transform you.

00:21:50.301 --> 00:21:52.723
Doing so by way of the Atama.

00:21:53.825 --> 00:21:54.605
Ha Atama,

00:21:54.685 --> 00:21:56.448
the bloody red man of the earth,

00:21:57.268 --> 00:21:59.869
or unto the ground.

00:21:59.930 --> 00:22:01.230
From it and by it,

00:22:02.311 --> 00:22:06.576
you were obtained and will be received at

00:22:06.596 --> 00:22:07.517
a moment in time.

00:22:07.977 --> 00:22:09.878
Lakash, you were grasped.

00:22:10.862 --> 00:22:12.021
and will be collected.

00:22:12.061 --> 00:22:13.623
You were brought forth and will be

00:22:13.682 --> 00:22:15.943
received at the proper period.

00:22:17.923 --> 00:22:18.003
Now,

00:22:18.023 --> 00:22:21.525
this is because you are a collection of

00:22:21.565 --> 00:22:23.786
particles comprising matter,

00:22:24.786 --> 00:22:28.326
even grayish dust and ash.

00:22:28.926 --> 00:22:32.248
And among dust or by ash,

00:22:33.048 --> 00:22:34.888
you will return,

00:22:35.348 --> 00:22:37.410
either be brought back or restored

00:22:37.450 --> 00:22:40.030
forevermore.

00:22:40.070 --> 00:22:40.371
Shubh.

00:22:41.400 --> 00:22:43.882
you will be turned back again or changed

00:22:43.942 --> 00:22:46.223
and transformed with ongoing implications

00:22:47.163 --> 00:22:47.884
throughout time.

00:22:49.246 --> 00:22:51.307
Profoundly stated in Baba Rashid in the

00:22:51.346 --> 00:22:53.689
beginning, the third chapter of the Torah,

00:22:54.148 --> 00:22:56.310
Genesis three, nineteen.

00:22:58.972 --> 00:22:59.753
Now in the garden.

00:23:03.096 --> 00:23:05.298
They had been given everything they needed

00:23:05.597 --> 00:23:07.058
for a joyous and fulfilling,

00:23:07.118 --> 00:23:09.161
even meaningful and productive life, but.

00:23:10.267 --> 00:23:11.949
They simply offered nothing back in

00:23:11.989 --> 00:23:12.388
return.

00:23:14.211 --> 00:23:16.573
That made them parasites, not partners.

00:23:19.776 --> 00:23:22.698
And that situation was not conducive to a

00:23:22.778 --> 00:23:26.020
meaningful relationship or sustained

00:23:26.061 --> 00:23:26.461
growth.

00:23:28.983 --> 00:23:29.484
Therefore,

00:23:29.545 --> 00:23:31.346
now that we are out on our own,

00:23:31.567 --> 00:23:33.969
there would be more thorns than fruit.

00:23:34.789 --> 00:23:38.851
The vegetation would be seeking to protect

00:23:38.911 --> 00:23:41.711
itself from being eaten, such that we,

00:23:43.133 --> 00:23:44.292
in looking for food,

00:23:44.333 --> 00:23:46.773
would have to work and adapt our

00:23:46.814 --> 00:23:48.875
environment to our needs.

00:23:50.055 --> 00:23:52.036
Man would have to learn to work to

00:23:52.076 --> 00:23:54.797
be useful and to become valuable,

00:23:54.856 --> 00:23:59.077
or he would die sooner rather than later.

00:24:02.798 --> 00:24:05.280
The contrast remains palpable.

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:09.282
Rather than labor harmoniously in Gan Eden

00:24:09.343 --> 00:24:10.903
with Yahweh, making it better,

00:24:11.484 --> 00:24:13.465
thereby protecting and perfecting it,

00:24:14.226 --> 00:24:15.446
as God had intended,

00:24:15.487 --> 00:24:16.887
they contributed nothing.

00:24:17.969 --> 00:24:22.211
Instead of a combined effort to make us

00:24:22.471 --> 00:24:23.011
all better,

00:24:23.051 --> 00:24:26.614
the first time they were shown lifting a

00:24:26.653 --> 00:24:30.155
finger was to do precisely what they had

00:24:30.175 --> 00:24:31.196
been asked to reject.

00:24:33.795 --> 00:24:35.996
As a result, from now on,

00:24:36.036 --> 00:24:39.198
their focus would be on the more immediate

00:24:39.878 --> 00:24:42.180
and mundane issues of survival.

00:24:43.601 --> 00:24:44.461
The Earth was good,

00:24:45.162 --> 00:24:47.782
the most conducive planet to life in the

00:24:47.883 --> 00:24:48.423
universe.

00:24:49.364 --> 00:24:50.285
But nonetheless,

00:24:51.546 --> 00:24:54.827
bad outcomes lurked behind every prickly

00:24:54.867 --> 00:24:55.147
bush.

00:24:58.509 --> 00:25:00.510
With the sparse knowledge they possessed,

00:25:01.431 --> 00:25:02.271
they would either make

00:25:03.964 --> 00:25:04.806
good, better,

00:25:05.846 --> 00:25:09.028
or they would make bad worse.

00:25:10.169 --> 00:25:11.410
This is what they had chosen for

00:25:11.450 --> 00:25:13.310
themselves, and it was only fair.

00:25:14.172 --> 00:25:16.113
Having disregarded Yahweh's guidance,

00:25:16.153 --> 00:25:20.096
there would be a less appealing menu,

00:25:20.996 --> 00:25:23.678
and effort would be required to prepare it

00:25:23.698 --> 00:25:24.499
for consumption.

00:25:26.380 --> 00:25:27.881
It would be rough out there.

00:25:29.041 --> 00:25:32.644
Even in an environment designed and finely

00:25:32.703 --> 00:25:33.765
tuned for life,

00:25:35.588 --> 00:25:39.172
Out in the wild, even lazy lions die.

00:25:41.393 --> 00:25:43.815
And if the two sides of Lakem,

00:25:44.375 --> 00:25:48.698
bread and war, were relevant, boy,

00:25:48.758 --> 00:25:51.440
is it ever applicable now.

00:25:53.622 --> 00:25:56.884
The divergent definitions of Lakem would

00:25:56.943 --> 00:25:58.444
come to be the story of man,

00:25:58.825 --> 00:25:59.526
bread and war,

00:26:01.146 --> 00:26:02.587
the hallmark of civilization.

00:26:04.923 --> 00:26:06.483
Bread or war.

00:26:08.986 --> 00:26:11.268
It would remain this way with our history

00:26:11.347 --> 00:26:14.089
demonstrating that bread would bring

00:26:14.150 --> 00:26:16.872
humans together and war would tear mankind

00:26:16.912 --> 00:26:17.291
apart.

00:26:18.012 --> 00:26:18.992
In the end, of course,

00:26:19.012 --> 00:26:24.317
we know that the prophets said that war

00:26:24.356 --> 00:26:27.980
would become global, even as many starved.

00:26:29.723 --> 00:26:31.125
And if not for the arrival of the

00:26:31.305 --> 00:26:32.987
ad, this restoring witness,

00:26:33.027 --> 00:26:35.429
the human experience would turn out to be

00:26:35.489 --> 00:26:35.909
for naught.

00:26:37.029 --> 00:26:39.471
Without the transformation of the ad,

00:26:39.531 --> 00:26:41.854
this eternal testimony provides,

00:26:43.195 --> 00:26:45.617
humans would forever remain estranged from

00:26:45.678 --> 00:26:45.978
God,

00:26:46.659 --> 00:26:49.661
ill-equipped to ever be trusted off this

00:26:49.701 --> 00:26:50.122
planet.

00:26:53.144 --> 00:26:54.484
Now, mixing his metaphors,

00:26:54.605 --> 00:26:57.367
as is Yahweh's custom, ha-adamah,

00:26:58.390 --> 00:27:03.132
That gave rise to Adam and the Dan

00:27:04.133 --> 00:27:08.494
and it's at tree as the ad,

00:27:08.535 --> 00:27:12.156
the restoring witness is going to serve to

00:27:12.196 --> 00:27:14.137
determine whether a man returns to the

00:27:14.157 --> 00:27:17.400
garden or to the dust of the earth

00:27:19.881 --> 00:27:20.361
is man,

00:27:20.421 --> 00:27:22.582
nothing more than a collection of earth

00:27:22.602 --> 00:27:25.983
and particles physically as a body.

00:27:27.208 --> 00:27:28.928
Or is he to be restored as a

00:27:29.008 --> 00:27:30.608
soul and to fellowship with God?

00:27:32.689 --> 00:27:35.349
Who among us will be purged by the

00:27:35.509 --> 00:27:37.349
ash of ha-adamah, parah,

00:27:39.030 --> 00:27:40.391
rather than remaining dirty,

00:27:41.971 --> 00:27:43.231
retaining their filth?

00:27:44.112 --> 00:27:45.951
Will you be among ha-adam,

00:27:47.092 --> 00:27:49.173
allowed to return to Gan Eden,

